column2: SELECT TOP # sp.objID,  sp.ra,  sp.dec, sp.plateID AS plateID, sp.plate AS plate,  sp.mjd AS mjd, sp.fiberID AS fiberID, /*gsl.sigma_balmer AS sigma,*/ /*gse.bptclass AS bpt,*/ sp.z AS Z, sp.zErr AS Z_Err, sp.psfmag_u, sp.psfmag_g, sp.psfmag_r, sp.psfmag_i, sp.psfmag_z FROM specPhotoALL AS sp  /*JOIN galSpecExtra AS gse ON (sp.specObjID = gse.specObjID)*/ /*INNER JOIN galSpecLine AS gsl ON (sp.specObjID = gsl.specObjID)*/ WHERE (sp.class=&&&) AND zWarning = # AND (sp.psfmag_u <= sp.psfmag_g) AND (sp.psfmag_u <= sp.psfmag_i) AND (sp.psfmag_u <= sp.psfmag_z) AND (sp.psfmag_u <= #) /*AND (sp.psfmag_g <= #) AND (sp.psfmag_r <= #)  AND (sp.psfmag_i <= #)  AND (sp.psfmag_z <= #)*/ AND (sp.psfmag_u >#) AND (sp.psfmag_g >#) AND (sp.psfmag_r >#) AND (sp.psfmag_i >#) AND (sp.psfmag_z >#) AND ((Z > #) AND (Z < #)) ORDER BY Z
